## ​ Environment variables
For local development, you need to set up the `TRIGGER_SECRET_KEY` environment variable.
This key authenticates your application with Trigger.dev.
1. Go to your project dashboard in Trigger.dev
2. Navigate to the “API Keys” page
3. Copy the **DEV** secret key
4. Add it to your local environment file:
